		<author>
			<name>Salvatore Messina</name>
		</author>
		<summary type="html">&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Io nelle mani del vento&lt;br /&gt;m'involo in spazi sconfinati. &lt;br /&gt;Intono canti &lt;br /&gt;inni a labbra chiuse&lt;br /&gt;mentre mi perdo &lt;br /&gt;tra luci di candele &lt;br /&gt;concerti dediti alle stelle. &lt;br /&gt;Estasiato è il cuore &lt;br /&gt;negli occhi di mio figlio. &lt;br /&gt;E' vivo.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;table style=&quot;border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%;&quot; cellpadding=&quot;8&quot;&gt;
&lt;tbody&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: left; width: 100%;&quot; colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt; &lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;tr&gt;
&lt;td style=&quot;text-align: left; width: 100%;&quot; colspan=&quot;2&quot;&gt;&lt;a title=&quot;Torna all'indice&quot; href=&quot;https://www.beneinst.it/sed-etiam.html&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://www.beneinst.it/images/Componenti/tornaindietro.png&quot; width=&quot;38&quot; height=&quot;49&quot; /&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/td&gt;
&lt;/tr&gt;
&lt;/tbody&gt;
&lt;/table&gt;</summary>
